{"tid":2130101,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳云：香港值得給共產黨統治","createTime":"2020-07-29T04:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T10:14:20.000Z","uid":5843,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"51230b84a512617a433b335298d410f4c6b55e44","tid":2130101,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"陳雲：（承上貼文）香港人比共產黨更邪惡，比大陸人更賤格。一場假瘟疫，令大家看清楚香港人的真面目。值回票價。<br />\n由於共產黨比香港人道德比較高尚，較為懂得約束權力及姑息小民，故此香港值得給共產黨統治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhqSZou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhqSZou.png&h=fc11474c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10158412700472225/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10158412700472225%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6WyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=9fc4c3f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10158412700472225/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"686940e762430ee335c7397cb22280ae2b8f8083","tid":2130101,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7bF0Nc.jpg&amp;h=2cd12e12&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"a29de5010c54b69ef0cf9b0d248f7fc4d0228ef2","tid":2130101,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3904f8cb0f6218da0988576cb54e00ecb5c5440d","tid":2130101,"uid":133743,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"其實國安法之後佢已經係咁投誠，算啦好冇"},{"pid":"f5e4dc7e52b54362491f930a178241a5a458d8b7","tid":2130101,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"神經病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6dc3b5f7fa96c1791853b35073bb2ede792036","tid":2130101,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"